nhc_headline: ...STRONG WINDS EXPECTED TO BEGIN IN THE AZORES WITHIN THE NEXT HOUR OR TWO...
summary: ...STRONG WINDS EXPECTED TO BEGIN IN THE AZORES WITHIN THE NEXT HOUR OR TWO... As of 12:00 AM GMT Fri Sep 26 the center of Gabrielle was located near 37.6, -30.5 with movement ENE at 30 mph. The minimum central pressure was 983 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 70 mph.
